title: Avanti 24in Gas Range DGR24P35
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Avanti DGR24P35 gas range.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/108014/Avanti-24-Stainless-Steel-Deluxe-Freestanding-Gas-Range-DGR24P3S.html 

Features:
Oven Capacity: 2.6 Cu. Ft.
Free Standing 24" Range
Bake / Broil Oven for Maximum Versatility
0-500 Degrees F Adjustable Bake Temperature
Four Sealed Burners for Easy Cleanup
(1) Rapid Cook Burner
(2) Regular Burners
(1) Simmer Burner
2 Oven Racks
Roll-Out Bottom Storage Drawer
See-Through Seamless Framed Glass Door
Digital Clock/ Kitchen Timer
Anti-Tip Bracket Included
LED Back-Lit Controls
Black Porcelain Enamel Oven Cavity
Professional Grade Cast-Iron Grates
Automatic Electronic Ignition
Waist High Broiler
Height: 37.5"
Width: 23.5"
Depth: 25.25"
